import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { UserService } from 'src/app/services/user.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-error', templateUrl: './error.component.html', styleUrls: ['./error.component.scss'], }) export class ErrorComponent implements OnInit { code: number; message: string; constructor(public router: Router, public auth: UserService) { const state = this.router.getCurrentNavigation()?.extras.state; this.code = state ? state.code : 500; this.message = state ? state.message : 'Something went wrong :('; } ngOnInit(): void { const cordCanvas: HTMLCanvasElement = document.getElementById( 'cord' ) as HTMLCanvasElement; const ctx = cordCanvas.getContext('2d')!; this.drawVisor(); this.animate(ctx); } drawVisor() { const canvas: HTMLCanvasElement = document.getElementById( 'visor' ) as HTMLCanvasElement; const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')!; ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(5, 45); ctx.bezierCurveTo(15, 64, 45, 64, 55, 45); ctx.lineTo(55, 20); ctx.bezierCurveTo(55, 15, 50, 10, 45, 10); ctx.lineTo(15, 10); ctx.bezierCurveTo(15, 10, 5, 10, 5, 20); ctx.lineTo(5, 45); ctx.fillStyle = '#2f3640'; ctx.strokeStyle = '#f5f6fa'; ctx.fill(); ctx.stroke(); } animate(ctx) { let y1 = 160; let y2 = 100; let y3 = 100; let y1Forward = true; let y2Forward = false; let y3Forward = true; ctx.clearRect(0, 0, innerWidth, innerHeight); ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(130, 170); ctx.bezierCurveTo(250, y1, 345, y2, 400, y3); ctx.strokeStyle = 'white'; ctx.lineWidth = 8; ctx.stroke(); if (y1 === 100) { y1Forward = true; } if (y1 === 300) { y1Forward = false; } if (y2 === 100) { y2Forward = true; } if (y2 === 310) { y2Forward = false; } if (y3 === 100) { y3Forward = true; } if (y3 === 317) { y3Forward = false; } y1Forward ? (y1 += 1) : (y1 -= 1); y2Forward ? (y2 += 1) : (y2 -= 1); y3Forward ? (y3 += 1) : (y3 -= 1); } dashboard() { this.router.navigate(['/dashboard']); } login() { this.router.navigate(['/login']); } register() { this.router.navigate(['/register']); } }
